---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Container } from '../../components/layout/Container';
import { Section } from '../../components/layout/Section';
import { Heading } from '../../components/ui/Heading';
import { Button } from '../../components/ui/Button';
import { StatCounter } from '../../components/ui/StatCounter';
import { CTASection } from '../../components/sections/CTASection';

const city = 'Seattle';
const state = 'Washington';
const stateAbbr = 'WA';
---

<BaseLayout
  title={`Google Ads Management ${city}, ${stateAbbr} - ProfitSEM`}
  description={`Top-rated Google Ads agency in ${city}. Profit-focused PPC management for ${city} businesses. 90-day guarantee. No contracts.`}
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <Section background="gradient" spacing="xl">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center text-white">
        <Heading as="h1" size="6xl" className="mb-6">
          Google Ads Management in {city}
        </Heading>
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 mb-8">
          Turn Google Ads into profit for your {city} business. No contracts. Just results in 90 days.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <Button variant="secondary" size="lg" href="/free-analysis">
            Get Free Profit Analysis
          </Button>
          <Button variant="ghost" size="lg" className="text-white border-white/30" href="/contact">
            Contact Us
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>

  <!-- Local Stats -->
  <Section background="white" spacing="lg">
    <Container>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
        <div>
          <StatCounter value="59" suffix="+" label={`${city} Clients`} variant="success" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <StatCounter value="294" suffix="%" label="Average ROI" variant="success" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <StatCounter prefix="$" value="2.1M" label="Client Revenue (Monthly)" variant="primary" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <StatCounter value="4.9" suffix="/5" label="Google Rating" variant="success" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>

  <!-- Local Benefits -->
  <Section background="gray" spacing="xl">
    <Container size="lg">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <Heading as="h2" size="4xl" className="mb-6">
            Why {city} Businesses Choose ProfitSEM
          </Heading>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Deep {city} Market Knowledge</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  We understand the {city} market—from Capitol Hill to Bellevue, from tech giants to innovative startups. Our strategies account for {city}'s sophisticated tech ecosystem, competitive landscape, and what actually drives conversions in {stateAbbr}.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Profit-Focused Approach</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Unlike typical {city} agencies that charge percentage fees, we use flat-rate pricing aligned with your profit goals. We make money when you make money—not when you spend money.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Pacific Time Zone Support</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Our {city} clients get dedicated account managers in {stateAbbr} time zone. No East Coast delays. No offshore support. We work when you work.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">90-Day Guarantee</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  We improve your Google Ads ROI within 90 days or you get a full refund. That's our promise to {city} businesses.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-xl">
          <Heading as="h3" size="2xl" className="mb-6">
            Industries We Serve in {city}
          </Heading>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>Cloud/SaaS</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>E-commerce (Amazon Ecosystem)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>AI/ML</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>Cybersecurity</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>Gaming/Entertainment</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>Professional Services</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Don't see your industry? We work with {city} businesses across all sectors.
            </p>
            <Button variant="primary" size="md" fullWidth href="/contact">
              Schedule Free Consultation
            </Button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>

  <!-- Local Testimonial -->
  <Section background="white" spacing="lg">
    <Container size="md">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-6">
          {[1,2,3,4,5].map(() => (
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
            </svg>
          ))}
        </div>

        <blockquote class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-6 italic">
          "Our Seattle-based e-commerce business was struggling to compete against Amazon's ad dominance. ProfitSEM found untapped niches and cut our CPA by 61% while tripling sales. Finally profitable on Google Ads."
        </blockquote>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
            LW
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold">Lisa Wang</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Founder, {city} E-commerce Co.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>

  <!-- Local SEO Content -->
  <Section background="gray" spacing="lg">
    <Container size="lg">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <Heading as="h2" size="3xl" className="mb-6">
          Google Ads Services for {city} Businesses
        </Heading>

        <p>
          {city} is a major tech hub and home to global giants like Amazon and Microsoft. With a thriving economy spanning cloud computing, e-commerce, AI/ML, and gaming, the competition for digital advertising is intense—especially in highly competitive B2B and tech sectors.
        </p>

        <p>
          That's where ProfitSEM comes in. We've helped over 55 {city} businesses across Capitol Hill, Bellevue, and the greater Puget Sound area turn Google Ads from a cost center into their #1 profit driver—with an average ROI of 294%.
        </p>

        <Heading as="h3" size="2xl" className="mb-4 mt-8">
          Our {city} Google Ads Process
        </Heading>

        <ol class="space-y-4">
          <li>
            <strong>Week 1-2: {city} Market Analysis</strong>
            <p>We analyze your {city} competitors, industry-specific search trends, and target audience behavior to build a profit-focused strategy. Whether you're competing in cloud/SaaS, e-commerce, or cybersecurity, we understand your market and the sophisticated targeting needed to succeed.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Week 3-4: Campaign Setup & Launch</strong>
            <p>We build conversion-optimized campaigns targeting high-intent {city} searchers and decision-makers. Our strategies account for {city}'s competitive market and the need to stand out against tech giants.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Week 5-12: Optimize & Scale</strong>
            <p>Weekly optimization based on performance data. We double down on what works and cut what doesn't. In the {city} market, precision and innovation win.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>

        <Heading as="h3" size="2xl" className="mb-4 mt-8">
          Why {city} Businesses Trust ProfitSEM
        </Heading>

        <ul>
          <li><strong>No Long-Term Contracts:</strong> Month-to-month service. Cancel anytime.</li>
          <li><strong>Flat-Rate Pricing:</strong> No percentage fees. Our incentives align with yours.</li>
          <li><strong>90-Day Guarantee:</strong> Improve ROI in 90 days or get a full refund.</li>
          <li><strong>{city} Support Team:</strong> Dedicated account managers in {stateAbbr} time zone.</li>
          <li><strong>Proven Results:</strong> Average 294% ROI for {city} clients.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-6 my-8">
          <p class="font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">
            Ready to grow your {city} business with Google Ads?
          </p>
          <p class="text-blue-800">
            Get a free profit analysis. We'll audit your current setup (or help you start from scratch) and show you exactly how we'll improve your ROI in the competitive {city} market.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <CTASection client:visible />
</BaseLayout>
